teesri aankh ( english : the third eye ) is a 2006 bollywood film starring sunny deol and amisha patel , and directed by harry baweja .   the film 's plot is inspired by michael powell 's controversial cult masterpiece peeping tom , however the story adds traditional bollywood flair including a love story and much less provocative themes than powell 's film .   the film is also inspired by the 1994 movie mute witness .   it was a box-office hit and did well overseas .